# GitHub Linguist language detection.
#
# This is a prose / spec repository: ~96% of files are Markdown (the spec, the
# design notes, and every eval run artifact), plus CSV/XLSX data. Linguist excludes
# Markdown (prose) and CSV/XLSX (data) from the language bar, so the only files it
# counts are the two eval-automation scripts under eval/runs/ — which made it read
# a misleading "JavaScript 100%".
#
# Mark those scripts as documentation so they're kept out of the language stats
# (they stay fully visible and searchable in diffs — this repo values auditability).
# With nothing left to count, the language bar reflects what this project is.
eval/runs/**/*.mjs linguist-documentation=true
